i can give you an example for now ("if playing" means not looking at a gui and actually playing the game)
def module auto-place
def desc "that when you left click on a obsidian/bedrock it automatically switches to a crystal and places it"

on left_click if playing {
  if target_block :bedrock,:obsidian {
    switch :end_crystal
    input use
  }
}